# 龙虾养成游戏 - 生图 Prompt 清单（Retro 8-bit Pixel Art 风格）

## 一、核心角色形象

### 1. 龙虾基础形象（6个成长阶段）

**Prompt 1.1 - 0-3岁（婴儿期）**
```
Retro 8-bit pixel art baby lobster character, chunky pixel blocks, limited 4-color palette (coral pink, cream, dark red, black outline), cute chibi proportions with oversized head, tiny body and claws, big round pixel eyes, friendly smile, bold 2px black pixel border, arcade game sprite aesthetic, flat 2D no gradients, 32x32px or 64x64px sprite, clean yellow background, tech brand mascot vibe
```

**Prompt 1.2 - 3-6岁（幼儿期）**
```
